The paper discusses the implementation of Industrial Symbiotic Networks (ISNs) as cooperative games, which falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). The paper also mentions the use of regulations and normative policies, which suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and social intelligence (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the use of normative multi-agent systems, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
